      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal equivalency mapping between validation test inputs and COU inputs is not required beyond qualitative documentation.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative mapping between validation operating conditions and COU operating envelope documented in the simulation report. Formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2 given the high geometric and operational similarity between validation and COU configurations."
